ORIGINAL WORKS
================================================================================

This project contains original works and innovations developed by William Finger,
including but not limited to:

1. TOON (Token-Oriented Object Notation) System
   - Hierarchical stack-based markdown parser
   - Token-aware compression algorithms
   - Multi-line list item parsing with continuation tracking
   - Path traversal prevention and security hardening
   - Glob pattern matching for selective file discovery

2. Project Architecture and Design
   - Full-stack application blueprint structure
   - Documentation organization system
   - Development workflows and tooling

3. Documentation and Content
   - Architecture guides
   - Setup instructions
   - Contributing guidelines
   - PRD templates and examples


